{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "KNPXEFQPF4VPCAHTMUHUAUNWYXNF6XLQ",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041032005",
    "title": "問・夢か現か？",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……――？\r\n水から上がったような気怠さが、全身を包み込んでいる。",
            "enText": "My body felt leaden… like I'd been dragged out \nof a swimming pool with my clothes on…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -312392425873387425
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -972769010257139779,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ゆっくりと瞼を開けると、静まり返った夜の教室と一緒に\r\nアグネスタキオンの姿が映り込んできた。",
            "enText": "Slowly I opened my eyes. I could make out the familiar \nshapes of a classroom in the darkness… and the figure \nof Agnes Tachyon standing before me…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -3759548185524024911
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1208151703115481143,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "発汗しているね。\r\n体温も……ふむ、見た感じ上昇しているようだ。",
            "enText": "Subject is sweating profusely. Body \ntemperature… appears to be rising.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 264,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "え……え！？",
                    "enText": "Eh… eh…!?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -2613704769218351523
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -6991875376552858856
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8796941963322613832,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "モルモットと言えど、熱放散反応はやはり人か。\r\nまぁ、そうでなくては困るんだが。",
            "enText": "Guinea pig you may be, but your body's febrile response is \nunquestionably human. Which is fine for our purposes, of course…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 247,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -5880693164758141216
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3289242130559339639
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6215817845876120522,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "自分の体を確認すると……\r\n見たこともないような実験器具に縛り付けられている！",
            "enText": "I looked down. My body was entangled with all manner of \nunfamiliar devices and strange instruments…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 4918945120760777252
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2761256186923746697,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "出会った時を思い出すねぇ。だが、あの時とは違う。\r\nここは私の、私だけの実験室。誰にも邪魔はされない！",
            "enText": "Ah, this is just like the day we first met…! Only \nthis time we have the laboratory all to ourselves. \nNobody will interfere with my experiment!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 424,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "実験室って……普通の教室だぞ！？",
                    "enText": "Laboratory…? But this is just an ordinary classroom…!",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "実験室って……普通の教室だよ！？",
                    "enText": "Laboratory…? But this is just an ordinary classroom…!",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 491000372535182783
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1018416671182801155
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 4737888714231772635
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2957729586543371033,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "いいや！　君が実験を望んだから私はここにいる！",
            "enText": "Ahh, not so! I am only here because you agreed \nto take part in this experiment.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 158,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 7905337529506874537
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -5215817088129777211
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -108678370699331179,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "この空間は君が用意してくれたものだ。\r\nであれば、実験室と呼ぶのが相応しいだろう？",
            "enText": "And this space is entirely of YOUR creation… \nso in that sense, it's quite accurate to call \nthis our \"laboratory\", don't you agree?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 253,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "意味がわからない……！",
                    "enText": "I don't understand…!",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 3094142253678818037
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4030392998187909315,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "アッハッハッハッ！　ならば理解するといい。\r\nいかなる事象も実験として受け入れるのがモルモットだと。",
            "enText": "A-hahahaa! Then understand this. A guinea pig's job is to be \nsubjected to whatever conditions the test requires.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 327,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": -8501486815731974825
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": 3501150596598799301
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 4892797547918359651
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7733278815087777960,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "君は自らモルモットに志願した。\r\n今更、実験前に都度コンセンサスを取れだなんて言うまい？",
            "enText": "And you volunteered to be my guinea pig, did you \nnot? If you wish to renegotiate the terms of your \nemployment, perhaps now is not the best time.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 4568553866457775611
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": 2812209854544160331
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5160809955927463611,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "限界を超え、ウマ娘の脚に秘められた可能性を導くには、\r\nたゆまぬ努力と研究……実験が必要なのだよ！",
            "enText": "To probe beyond the limits… to reveal the true potential of the \nUma Musume… this requires tireless effort and research, of which \ntesting is an indispensable part!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 328,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": -5123751473461974764
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5189275837465437118
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 4828662017011397619
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4482546014574763242,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "さて、出来たばかりの楽しいお薬を飲ませてあげよう。\r\n青く発光しているから、目でも楽しめるぞ。",
            "enText": "Now! Perhaps it's time I let you try a rather enjoyable new serum \nI have created. It has an intense blue glow which I think you \nwill find quite pleasing!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 302,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": 3417621635909080523
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3147046487660016952,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "クククッ……これで君の筋力は何倍にも増強され、\r\nどんな怪物をも凌駕する最高の肉体を手に入れることだろう！",
            "enText": "Heeheehee… and with this your muscular strength will increase \nseveral fold… Your body will be blessed with unimaginable \nstrength, strength surpassing the most fearsome monster…!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 397,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "！？",
                    "enText": "!?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -6864888262965448619
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": -7897992733912404818
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 7596151385525704939
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 55955850043294857,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "さぁ、口を開けたまえ。",
            "enText": "Now… open wide…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 104,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 7711349489253246507
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5698956229694913619
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7151807323467484326,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうなった彼女を止める術はない。\r\nそもそも、モルモットでいいと告げたのは自分だ。",
            "enText": "There was nothing I could do to stop her. She was right, after \nall. I was the one who volunteered to be her guinea pig.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 5566011792657021666
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 7571856583024008709
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5021938513482204201,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "覚悟を決めて、恐る恐る口を開けた――",
            "enText": "I gathered my resolve, closed my eyes… and opened my mouth…",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -8496820379452998858
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -3991859364380345405
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5477202920739485716,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "――おや、おはようモルモット君。",
            "enText": "Well, well. Good morning my little guinea pig.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 117,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": 3498384589484125485
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": 1057500058692377110
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": 7954274017390756849
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7549247036796375924,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "痛いくらいの光が目に飛び込んできた。\r\n……もしや、さっきまでの出来事は。",
            "enText": "The sunlight burned as it flooded my eyes. But \nthat must mean everything up to now had been…",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "あ、あれ……！？夢！？",
                    "enText": "H…… huh!? A dream…!?",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 8612164779985892445
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -5355664144951453332
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2697884726512357005,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "んん？　随分と怯えているね？　もしや悪夢でも見たのかい？",
            "enText": "Hmm? You seem troubled. Some kind of… nightmare, perhaps?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 199,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -8188371135008234064
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3038056438669743946
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2096808300149621367,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "光の量に変化はないはずだが、僅かに瞳孔が震えている。\r\nクククッ……興味が出たぞ。話してみるといい。",
            "enText": "Curious… the light level in here hasn't changed, but there is a \npronounced dilation in your pupils… Intriguing… most intriguing. \nWhy don't you tell me what you saw.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 340,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": 3356130297561274728
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -7763478520686691092
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3978726908861435035,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "夢のメカニズムは、いまだ謎の多い部分ではある。\r\nが、これを深層心理として考えると――",
            "enText": "There is still much we do not understand neurologically about the \ndreaming brain… But if we apply the principles of depth \npsychology to your experience…",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 261,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": 2751881476309641181
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1070194173740891996
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7805886863436623062,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "君の潜在意識にいる私は\r\n『人の話を聞かず勝手に実験をするウマ娘』、ということになるな。",
            "enText": "It seems as though you see me as an Uma Musume who \nmight at any moment subject you to horrifying experimentation, \nwithout warning or consent…!",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 275,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 213,
                    "pathId": -3252454612273774818
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 189,
                    "pathId": 6654937451622014267
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4152473569679005223,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "それにしても……そうか。夢の中の私がそんなことをねぇ。",
            "enText": "I see… that is the Agnes Tachyon that resides in your psyche.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 244,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ごめん、悪気はなくて……",
                    "enText": "Sorry I, uh… didn't mean anything by it…",
                    "nextBlock": 24
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ごめんね、悪気はなくて……",
                    "enText": "Sorry I, uh… didn't mean anything by it…",
                    "nextBlock": 24
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -5310487903718647102
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -766777341398214651
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6797388582048949691,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ククッ……わざわざ『口を開けろ』、とは。\r\n夢の中の私は、随分と面倒なことをするな。",
            "enText": "Hahaha…! To think that I would go to the trouble of ASKING you to \nopen your mouth! The Agnes Tachyon of your dreams clearly has \nmore time to waste than I do…",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 308,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 2439259827392649312
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 2500459759544831021
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3384418409912845986,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "モルモットに実験可否の返事も意見も聞く必要はないだろうに！",
            "enText": "One does not ask the guinea pig's PERMISSION to \ncommence the experiment, good gracious no!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 176,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ",
                    "enText": "Um.",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 7872833321381730915
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1893914891023848736
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 3447455448641741484
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9020941135863293437,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ハッハッハッ！　何をポカンとしているんだい。\r\n自身が被験体であることを忘れていたのかい？",
            "enText": "Hahahaha! Oh, what are you gawping at now? Did you forget that \nyou willingly donated your body to my research?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 265,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": 5167615284378992518
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 8243028635492212351
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 2300792555566846012
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9082790388293693049,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "いやしかし先程は実に惜しかった。あともう少しで\r\n安らか～に眠る君の口に薬品βを流し込めたのに。",
            "enText": "And I was so close, too. Why, a few moments longer and you would \nhave been sleeping like a baby… and I could have slipped serum \nbeta down your throat without you even noticing!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 327,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ！？",
                    "enText": "Huh…!?",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 245,
                    "pathId": 6775084452235760961
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": 4256933915574695555
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8149968490793078843,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "あぁこれは、言っておくけれど私なりの慈悲というやつだよ？\r\n薬品βは効果こそ望めるものの味が最悪でね。",
            "enText": "Ah, yes, this. For what it's worth, on this occasion I was \nactually trying to do you a service. I have high hopes for serum \nbeta's effectiveness, you see, but it tastes quite revolting…",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 341,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": 7337661284351157372
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 4929872376131678219
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1921452719300023946,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "けれど零すだのなんだの気にしながら120ミリリットルを\r\n流し込むより、人類に文明をもたらしたその両の手を使ってくれ。",
            "enText": "Oh well, now that you're awake I won't need to worry about \nspilling these 120ml… Because you can use those precious \nopposable digits of yours to do the job yourself!",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 304,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6297773067920710628
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1412067826725482687
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9143802424942040634,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "無論、当然、その方が私は楽だからね！！",
            "enText": "It certainly makes MY life easier… and that's what counts.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 134,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いや、あの――",
                    "enText": "Wait, I… um…",
                    "nextBlock": 31
